<p>The biggest challenge that remains for Uganda is low vaccination rates, where the reported vaccinated persons is less than 0.01% . The hope is that there will be more  equitable access to the vaccines and help tackle the pandemic as more vaccine donations come from China, Europe, and the USA.</p>

